  <brief_title>ABX-EGF (a Monoclonal Antibody) Given to Patients With Prostate Cancer With or Without Tumor in Other Parts of the Body</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Clinical Trial Evaluating the Safety and Efficacy of ABX-EGF in Patients With Hormone Resistant Prostate Cancer With or Without Metastasis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
