  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A clinical trial examining the safety and effectiveness of ABX-EGF when given to patients
      with prostate cancer with or without tumor in other parts of the body.

      Patients will be treated for a maximum of 48 doses (6 treatment courses; 8 doses per course)
      or until evidence of progressive disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
